--------------------------------
Dependencies
--------------------------------

SOLD requires the following:

-- matplotlib (sudo apt-get install python-matplotlib)
-- numpy (sudo apt-get install python-numpy)
-- Atomic simulation environment (installation instructions below)

--------------------------------
ASE installation instructions
--------------------------------

To install the atomic simulation environment, run the following

    sudo bash -c 'echo "deb http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/home:/dtufys/xUbuntu_14.04 /" > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/home_dtufys.sources.list'
    wget http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/home:/dtufys/xUbuntu_14.04/Release.key && sudo apt-key add Release.key && rm Release.key
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get -y install python-ase

--------------------------------
Installing SOLD
--------------------------------

After installing the dependencies, just run sudo ./SETUP.sh in this directory


